00:35:38,550 --> 00:35:39,000
I...

595
00:35:39,280 --> 00:35:41,000
I didn't come back late on purpose.

596
00:35:41,000 --> 00:35:42,260
There's a little issue

597
00:35:42,480 --> 00:35:44,680
with the Industry and Commerce Bureau.

598
00:35:44,800 --> 00:35:45,600
What's wrong?

599
00:35:46,110 --> 00:35:47,320
Our application

600
00:35:47,360 --> 00:35:48,560
didn't get approved.

601
00:35:48,880 --> 00:35:50,680
I think it's quite troublesome.

602
00:35:50,790 --> 00:35:52,450
I went to ask someone for help.

603
00:35:52,630 --> 00:35:53,590
Otherwise,

604
00:35:55,550 --> 00:35:56,880
we might be suspended

605
00:35:58,480 --> 00:35:59,820
and we might even have to compensate

606
00:35:59,820 --> 00:36:00,940
for the losses.

607
00:36:02,440 --> 00:36:03,000
This...

608
00:36:05,320 --> 00:36:05,960
This...

609
00:36:09,320 --> 00:36:10,110
Let's eat.

610
00:36:14,710 --> 00:36:15,320
By the way,

611
00:36:15,800 --> 00:36:17,480
make some time on Saturday.

612
00:36:18,110 --> 00:36:19,030
Mrs. Chen

613
00:36:19,280 --> 00:36:21,480
is going to introduce a young man to you.

614
00:36:21,960 --> 00:36:23,360
I've already checked him out.

615
00:36:23,360 --> 00:36:25,160
His conditions are pretty good.

616
00:36:25,800 --> 00:36:27,360
He's a good match for you.

617
00:36:30,550 --> 00:36:31,070
Mom.

618
00:36:31,330 --> 00:36:32,590
I can't go on Saturday.

619
00:36:33,510 --> 00:36:34,440
I have work to do.

620
00:36:41,840 --> 00:36:42,710
Don't think

621
00:36:43,710 --> 00:36:45,640
I don't know what you're thinking.

622
00:36:46,400 --> 00:36:47,840
If you had listened to me,

623
00:36:48,070 --> 00:36:48,710
now,

624
00:36:49,280 --> 00:36:49,960
would you be stuck

625
00:36:49,960 --> 00:36:51,550
working as some temporary teacher

626
00:36:51,550 --> 00:36:53,080
at that ridiculous school?

627
00:36:53,550 --> 00:36:54,630
Study meteorology

628
00:36:56,630 --> 00:36:58,800
to become a wild man in the mountains?

629
00:37:01,510 --> 00:37:02,550
For a girl,

630
00:37:03,230 --> 00:37:05,030
there are two big things in life.

631
00:37:05,800 --> 00:37:07,230
The first one, college,

632
00:37:07,480 --> 00:37:08,880
was already ruined by you.

633
00:37:08,880 --> 00:37:10,480
As for the second, marriage,

634
00:37:10,480 --> 00:37:11,810
you have to listen to me.

635
00:37:12,000 --> 00:37:13,070
On this matter,

636
00:37:13,480 --> 00:37:15,280
there's no room for discussion.

637
00:37:21,070 --> 00:37:22,400
I'll make it clear then.

638
00:37:23,550 --> 00:37:24,960
I won't go on a blind date.

639
00:37:27,840 --> 00:37:28,880
No blind date?

640
00:37:29,590 --> 00:37:30,720
What's your reason?

641
00:37:32,230 --> 00:37:33,150
Tell me.

642
00:37:35,440 --> 00:37:36,640
I've had a boyfriend.

643
00:37:40,630 --> 00:37:41,150
Tong.

644
00:37:42,070 --> 00:37:43,270
When did that happen?

645
00:37:43,800 --> 00:37:45,230
You didn't tell me that.

646
00:37:47,190 --> 00:37:47,880
Who is he?

647
00:37:48,230 --> 00:37:49,440
What's his name?

648
00:37:49,760 --> 00:37:51,000
Which university does he graduate from?

649
00:37:51,000 --> 00:37:51,860
What does he do?

650
00:37:51,960 --> 00:37:53,290
What does his family do?

651
00:37:55,230 --> 00:37:56,360
His name is Su Muxin.

652
00:38:00,320 --> 00:38:00,780
Then...

653
00:38:04,280 --> 00:38:05,590
Which Su Muxin?

654
00:38:06,230 --> 00:38:06,760
Shen Jing.

655
00:38:06,760 --> 00:38:08,840
This name sounds familiar.

656
00:38:08,840 --> 00:38:09,300
Enough.

657
00:38:09,460 --> 00:38:10,460
Stop pretending.

658
00:38:14,150 --> 00:38:16,080
That's her high school classmate.

659
00:38:17,280 --> 00:38:18,710
I remember now.

660
00:38:19,280 --> 00:38:20,510
Tong, is he that old classmate

661
00:38:20,510 --> 00:38:22,080
you met when you went

662
00:38:22,360 --> 00:38:24,550
to the Industry and Commerce Bureau
with me?

663
00:38:24,550 --> 00:38:26,320
You fell in love so soon.

664
00:38:26,800 --> 00:38:28,000
I didn't expect that.

665
00:38:31,960 --> 00:38:33,290
But this is a good thing.

666
00:38:33,430 --> 00:38:34,440
That young man

667
00:38:34,470 --> 00:38:35,360
is quite nice.

668
00:38:36,030 --> 00:38:37,230
He's a civil servant.

669
00:38:37,250 --> 00:38:39,110
He's even a deputy section chief.

670
00:38:44,800 --> 00:38:47,330
Even a section chief
wouldn't be good enough.

671
00:39:07,760 --> 00:39:08,440
Muxin.

672
00:39:08,520 --> 00:39:09,360
Do you remember

673
00:39:09,360 --> 00:39:11,230
back when we were filling out
college applications,

674
00:39:11,230 --> 00:39:12,110
we planned

675
00:39:12,110 --> 00:39:13,480
to become wild men together?

676
00:39:13,480 --> 00:39:14,150
Of course.

677
00:39:14,230 --> 00:39:15,310
How could I forget?

678
00:39:17,400 --> 00:39:18,660
Back then, you said...

679
00:39:18,670 --> 00:39:19,930
Look at my poor memory.

680
00:39:21,800 --> 00:39:22,930
I brought it with me,

681
00:39:23,110 --> 00:39:24,770
but I just couldn't remember.

682
00:39:32,030 --> 00:39:32,550
Here.

683
00:39:33,230 --> 00:39:34,490
I found one over there.

684
00:39:39,440 --> 00:39:41,100
I don't like black umbrellas.

685
00:39:45,710 --> 00:39:46,640
Look over there.

686
00:39:47,110 --> 00:39:48,000
So beautiful.

687
00:39:48,710 --> 00:39:49,710
Is it cloud or fog?

688
00:39:56,920 --> 00:39:57,550
Tong.

689
00:40:02,840 --> 00:40:03,970
What's wrong, Tong?

690
00:40:06,030 --> 00:40:06,590
Nothing.

691
00:40:06,960 --> 00:40:08,290
It's too hot down there.

692
00:40:10,150 --> 00:40:10,880
Muxin.

693
00:40:18,070 --> 00:40:20,120
[Qu Tong, Muxin]

694
00:40:18,320 --> 00:40:19,590
Don't you dare lose this ring.

695
00:40:19,590 --> 00:40:20,320
Not for a lifetime!

696
00:40:20,320 --> 00:40:22,120
Whoever loses it is a total dork.

697
00:40:23,200 --> 00:40:23,800
Thumb promise!

698
00:40:23,800 --> 00:40:24,660
Thumb promise!

699
00:40:30,800 --> 00:40:31,600
What's wrong?

700
00:40:59,320 --> 00:40:59,840
Dad.

701
00:41:00,280 --> 00:41:01,920
I really don't want to get married.

702
00:41:01,920 --> 00:41:02,900
It's already this late.

703
00:41:02,900 --> 00:41:04,450
What on earth is going on?

704
00:41:05,000 --> 00:41:06,550
Explain to me, okay?

705
00:41:07,110 --> 00:41:07,960
I think he's different

706
00:41:07,960 --> 00:41:08,760
from before.

707
00:41:11,480 --> 00:41:13,280
He's not the Su Muxin he once was.

708
00:41:18,480 --> 00:41:18,920
Alright.

709
00:41:18,920 --> 00:41:19,760
Now, if we may,

710
00:41:19,800 --> 00:41:20,630
let the two newlyweds

711
00:41:20,630 --> 00:41:22,360
exchange their token of love.

712
00:41:29,320 --> 00:41:30,550
This tiny ring

713
00:41:30,590 --> 00:41:31,480
doesn't just glimmer

714
00:41:31,480 --> 00:41:32,810
with the sheen of metal.

715
00:41:32,840 --> 00:41:33,590
It's more a symbol

716
00:41:33,590 --> 00:41:35,130
of their love.

717
00:41:36,360 --> 00:41:37,920
People change.

718
00:41:38,360 --> 00:41:39,280
In this world,

719
00:41:39,320 --> 00:41:40,190
the only constant

720
00:41:40,190 --> 00:41:41,480
is that everything is changing.

721
00:41:41,480 --> 00:41:42,410
Isn't that true?

722
00:41:42,550 --> 00:41:43,400
Next, let's invite the bride

723
00:41:43,400 --> 00:41:45,000
to place her token of love

724
00:41:45,030 --> 00:41:46,920
on the groom's finger.

725
00:42:06,190 --> 00:42:07,450
He used his position

726
00:42:07,630 --> 00:42:09,160
to save our family factory.

727
00:42:09,920 --> 00:42:10,880
He has the ability

728
00:42:10,880 --> 00:42:12,480
to make your life better.

729
00:42:13,070 --> 00:42:14,470
Shouldn't you marry him?

730
00:42:25,800 --> 00:42:26,400
Tong.

731
00:42:27,000 --> 00:42:28,030
You're the one

732
00:42:28,550 --> 00:42:30,810
who wanted to date him in the first place.

733
00:42:31,440 --> 00:42:32,540
I think

734
00:42:32,920 --> 00:42:34,590
this is also your best choice.

735
00:42:36,000 --> 00:42:37,860
You'll have a better life than me.

736
00:42:41,710 --> 00:42:43,390
Don't let me down completely.

737
00:42:58,070 --> 00:42:58,960
Alright. As we can see,

738
00:42:58,960 --> 00:42:59,840
our bride is already

739
00:42:59,840 --> 00:43:01,190
moved to tears.

740
00:43:01,230 --> 00:43:03,580
She needs even more of your applause!

741
00:43:08,880 --> 00:43:10,280
This token of love

742
00:43:10,320 --> 00:43:10,920
will also

743
00:43:10,960 --> 00:43:12,480
accompany them
throughout their entire lives,

744
00:43:12,480 --> 00:43:13,880
witnessing every moment

745
00:43:13,920 --> 00:43:15,190
of happiness.

746
00:43:16,030 --> 00:43:17,150
Perfect! The ceremony is now complete.

747
00:43:17,150 --> 00:43:18,280
On this happy

748
00:43:18,320 --> 00:43:19,320
and joyful day,

749
00:43:19,360 --> 00:43:20,690
we all witness together

750
00:43:20,710 --> 00:43:23,440
the birth of a beautiful love.

751
00:43:33,740 --> 00:43:40,890
[Happiness]

752
00:43:41,590 --> 00:43:42,150
Tong.

753
00:43:43,480 --> 00:43:44,610
Where are you going?

754
00:43:46,880 --> 00:43:47,880
To buy something.

755
00:43:51,950 --> 00:43:53,040
I'll go with you.

756
00:43:53,230 --> 00:43:54,960
I can help you carry things too.

757
00:43:55,030 --> 00:43:56,110
Anyway, I don't have much

758
00:43:56,110 --> 00:43:57,040
to do these days.

759
00:43:58,320 --> 00:43:59,030
No need.

760
00:44:00,960 --> 00:44:02,050
I can go by myself.

761
00:44:04,550 --> 00:44:05,560
Did I do something

762
00:44:05,590 --> 00:44:06,200
wrong

763
00:44:06,230 --> 00:44:07,490
that made you unhappy?

764
00:44:09,000 --> 00:44:09,630
Tell me.

765
00:44:10,400 --> 00:44:11,190
I can fix it.

766
00:44:22,020 --> 00:44:23,150
I'm not blaming you.

767
00:44:25,070 --> 00:44:26,310
And I'm not unhappy.

768
00:44:28,960 --> 00:44:30,960
I just want to go out for a walk alone.

769
00:44:35,840 --> 00:44:36,480
Fine.

770
00:44:39,530 --> 00:44:40,670
Wait a minute.

771
00:44:51,070 --> 00:44:52,280
The sun is strong outside.

772
00:44:52,280 --> 00:44:53,110
Don't get sunburnt.

773
00:44:53,110 --> 00:44:54,710
Take this umbrella with you.

774
00:44:59,580 --> 00:45:00,360
It's going to rain soon.

775
00:45:00,360 --> 00:45:01,420
Take this with you.

776
00:45:16,120 --> 00:45:17,040
A few days ago,

777
00:45:17,330 --> 00:45:19,550
I checked out
of the single staff dormitory.

778
00:45:19,550 --> 00:45:20,670
And I found this.

779
00:45:30,510 --> 00:45:31,910
I'll wait for you at home.

780
00:45:39,400 --> 00:45:40,450
Wait.

